snippet.title: PepeFrog is a pixel game about a crazy frog!
snippet.description:
Welcome to PepeFrog! Set a new world record in the crazy frog simulator with mechanics reminiscent of Doodle Jump to become the TOP-1 player in the world rankings!


Link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...​


Features of the game:
🎮 Sticky and long-lasting gameplay: play like a pro, jump over water lilies, earn coins, look for gifts, break records, but be careful, not every water lily can handle you!
🎨 Beautiful pixel art!
🐸 A large number of frogs of different characteristics!
🏆 Real-time world leaderboard!
🎁 Get unique prizes by opening collected gifts!
💰 Spend the received coins on unique frogs!
